                                  +---------------------------------+


Communication Flow
User Request Flow:
--> User requests www.griffinfamily.link/Resumes/Mike
--> DNS resolves to the ALB IP address
--> ALB forwards the request to the Kubernetes ingress controller
--> Ingress routes the request to web application service
--> Web app pods serve the content

Deployment Flow:
--> Push code to GitHub
--> GitHub Actions builds a new container image
--> Image is pushed to ECR
--> Helm chart values are updated with the new image tag
--> ArgoCD detects the change and updates the deployment
--> Kubernetes rolls out the new version
